arrow"></path></g></svg></a></div></div></div></div><div class="col col-lg-6 col-md-12"><div class="u-d-flex cc-vertical gap_1-5-1 u-h-100"><h2 class="h5">Customer Stories</h2><div class="swiper cc-nav w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="swiper-wrapper cc-nav w-dyn-items"><div style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/692646d687adbcaacae13ba7_7 (1).avif&quot;)" role="listitem" class="swiper-slide cc-nav u-wedge-top-right w-dyn-item"><div class="stories_card cc-nav"><img loading="lazy" src="/images/placeholder.svg" alt="" class="stories_logo w-dyn-bind-empty"/><h4 class="h5 u-color-primary-invert">Engineered power solutions for a public AI hyperscaler</h4><p class="u-color-secondary-invert">“Giga&#x27;s 7-week turnaround and custom engineering allowed us to scale up GPUs quickly.”</p></div></div><div style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/67f4a19c71717f352e12ce6d_1737059193933 1.avif&quot;)" role="listitem" class="swiper-slide cc-nav u-wedge-top-right w-dyn-item"><div class="stories_card cc-nav"><img loading="lazy" src="/images/placeholder.svg" alt="" class="stories_logo w-dyn-bind-empty"/><h4 class="h5 u-color-primary-invert">Delivered in-house manufactured equipment in record time to preserve energization timeline</h4><p class="u-color-secondary-invert">&quot;The equipment not only arrived on the tight timeline, but we&#x27;ve been extremely satisfied with the quality since the site was energized.&quot;</p></div></div><div style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/69d4315a218da915d18ff172_dji_fly_20250105_191612_0066_1762807834004_photo.avif&quot;)" role="listitem" class="swiper-slide cc-nav u-wedge-top-right w-dyn-item"><div class="stories_card cc-nav"><img loading="lazy" src="/images/placeholder.svg" alt="" class="stories_logo w-dyn-bind-empty"/><h4 class="h5 u-color-primary-invert">Energized 10MW in West Texas</h4><p class="u-color-secondary-invert">“Our electricians let us know multiple times how much they prefer the GIGA equipment to anything else they have installed. It’s the best of any single piece of infrastructure we ordered.”</p></div></div></div></div><div class="u-d-flex cc-vertical cc-gap-24"><div class="swiper-pagination"><div class="u-d-flex cc-horizontal cc-gap-16"><div class="swiper-arrows cc-blocks cc-prev cc-navigation"><div class="u-icon cc-24"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M13.5 7L8.5 12L13.5 17" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div><div class="swiper-arrows cc-blocks cc-next cc-navigation"><div class="u-icon cc-24"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M10.5 7L15.5 12L10.5 17" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></nav></div><div data-hover="false" data-delay="0" class="nav_dropdown w-dropdown"><div class="nav_dropdown-toggle w-dropdown-toggle"><div class="eyebrow">resources</div><div class="nav_dropdown-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="u-icon cc-24"><path d="M7 9.5L12 14.5L17 9.5" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div><nav class="nav_dropdown-container cc-full w-dropdown-list"><div class="nav_dropdown-inner cc-support"><div class="u-w-100 u-h-100"><h2 class="eyebrow u-mb-1-5">Resources</h2><div data-current="Blog" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="0" data-duration-out="0" class="nav_dropdown-tabs w-tabs"><div data-nav-move-target="resources" class="nav_dropdown-tabs-menu w-tab-menu"><a data-w-tab="Blog" class="nav_dropdown-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current"><div class="u-icon cc-24 u-color-brand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M6 0H16.4142L22 5.58579V20H6V0ZM4 4V22H18V24H2V4H4ZM18 14V16H10V14H18ZM10 12H14V10H10V12Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div><div>Blog</div></a><a data-w-tab="Guides" class="nav_dropdown-tabs-link w-inline-blo